## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-404">某些 Windows 窗体控件可以使用基于 [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdi](~/includes/ndptecgdi-md.md)] 图形库的 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextRenderer> 类或基于 [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] 图形库的 <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> 类来呈现其文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-404">Certain Windows Forms controls can render their text using either the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextRenderer> class, which is based on the [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdi](~/includes/ndptecgdi-md.md)] graphics library, or the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> class, which is based on the [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] graphics library.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-405">此更改是在 [!INCLUDE[dnprdnlong](~/includes/dnprdnlong-md.md)] 中进行的，因为 [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)]的性能和本地化问题。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-405">This change was made in the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnlong](~/includes/dnprdnlong-md.md)] because of performance and localization issues with [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-406">使用 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.SetCompatibleTextRenderingDefault%2A> 为支持的控件设置 `UseCompatibleTextRendering` 属性的默认值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-406">Use <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.SetCompatibleTextRenderingDefault%2A> to set the default value of the `UseCompatibleTextRendering` property for controls that support it.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-407">`UseCompatibleTextRendering` 属性旨在提供 Windows 窗体控件之间的视觉兼容性，这些控件使用 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextRenderer> 类呈现文本，并使用 [!INCLUDE[net_v11_short](~/includes/net-v11-short-md.md)] 类 [!INCLUDE[net_v10_short](~/includes/net-v10-short-md.md)] 和 <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> 执行自定义文本呈现的应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-407">The `UseCompatibleTextRendering` property is intended to provide visual compatibility between Windows Forms controls that render text using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextRenderer> class and [!INCLUDE[net_v10_short](~/includes/net-v10-short-md.md)] and [!INCLUDE[net_v11_short](~/includes/net-v11-short-md.md)] applications that perform custom text rendering using the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-408">在大多数情况下，如果你的应用程序不是从 [!INCLUDE[net_v10_short](~/includes/net-v10-short-md.md)] 或 [!INCLUDE[net_v11_short](~/includes/net-v11-short-md.md)]升级，则建议你将 `UseCompatibleTextRendering` 设置为默认值 "`false`"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-408">In most cases, if your application is not being upgraded from [!INCLUDE[net_v10_short](~/includes/net-v10-short-md.md)] or [!INCLUDE[net_v11_short](~/includes/net-v11-short-md.md)], it is recommended that you leave `UseCompatibleTextRendering` set to the default value of `false`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-409">[!INCLUDE[dnprdnlong](~/includes/dnprdnlong-md.md)] 中引入了基于 [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdi](~/includes/ndptecgdi-md.md)] 的 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextRenderer> 类以提高性能，使文本更好地显示，并改善对国际字体的支持。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-409">The [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdi](~/includes/ndptecgdi-md.md)] based <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextRenderer> class was introduced in the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnlong](~/includes/dnprdnlong-md.md)] to improve performance, make text look better, and improve support for international fonts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-410">在 [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]的早期版本中，将使用基于 [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] 的 <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> 类来执行所有文本呈现。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-410">In earlier versions of the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)], the [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] based <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> class was used to perform all text rendering.</span></span> [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdi](~/includes/ndptecgdi-md.md)] <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-411">计算不同于 [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)]的字符间距和自动换行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-411">calculates character spacing and word wrapping differently from [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-412">在使用 <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> 类呈现文本的 Windows 窗体应用程序中，这可能会导致使用 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextRenderer> 的控件的文本与应用程序中的其他文本显示不相同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-412">In a Windows Forms application that uses the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> class to render text, this could cause the text for controls that use <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextRenderer> to appear different from the other text in the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-413">若要解决这种不兼容性问题，你可以将 `UseCompatibleTextRendering` 属性设置为 `true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-413">To resolve this incompatibility, you can set the `UseCompatibleTextRendering` property to `true`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-414">若要将 `UseCompatibleTextRendering` 设置为应用程序中所有支持的控件 `true`，请使用 `true`的参数调用 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.SetCompatibleTextRenderingDefault%2A> 方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-414">To set `UseCompatibleTextRendering` to `true` for all supported controls in the application, call the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.SetCompatibleTextRenderingDefault%2A> method with a parameter of `true`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-415">如果 Windows 窗体代码承载于其他应用程序（如 Internet Explorer）中，则永远不应调用此方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-415">You should never call this method if your Windows Forms code is hosted in another application, such as Internet Explorer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-416">仅在独立 Windows 窗体应用程序中调用此方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-416">Only call this method in stand-alone Windows Forms applications.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-417">若要设置 [!INCLUDE[vbprvblong](~/includes/vbprvblong-md.md)] 或更高版本中 `UseCompatibleTextRendering` 的默认值，请参阅 <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.ApplicationServices.WindowsFormsApplicationBase.UseCompatibleTextRendering%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-417">To set the default value for `UseCompatibleTextRendering` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvblong](~/includes/vbprvblong-md.md)] or later, see <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.ApplicationServices.WindowsFormsApplicationBase.UseCompatibleTextRendering%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-418">在 [!INCLUDE[csprcslong](~/includes/csprcslong-md.md)] 或更高版本中，将在 Program.cs 文件中自动生成对 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.SetCompatibleTextRenderingDefault%2A> 的调用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-418">In [!INCLUDE[csprcslong](~/includes/csprcslong-md.md)] or later, a call to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.SetCompatibleTextRenderingDefault%2A> is automatically generated in the Program.cs file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f0fff-419">若要更改文本呈现默认值，请修改生成的代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f0fff-419">To change the text rendering default, modify the generated code.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
static class Program  
{  
    /// <summary>  
    /// The main entry point for the application.  
    /// </summary>  
    [STAThread]  
    static void Main()  
    {  
        Application.EnableVisualStyles();  
        Application.SetCompatibleTextRenderingDefault(false);  
        Application.Run(new Form1());  
    }  
}  
```
